\v 11 \x - \xo 2:11 \xt Luk 9:32; Jon 1:14; 4:54; 11:40\x*Kar mirakel…®n arazir Iesus faragham amizim. A Galilin Distrigh…®n aven itir nguibam Kanan, mirakel…®n arazir kam gami. Ez…® mirakel…®n kam…®n, Iesus bar uan gavgavir ekiam aka. Ez…® an suren gumaziba an ganigha egha n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an iti.
