\v 1 \x - \xo 4:1-3 \xt Jon 3:22; 3:26\x*Ez…® Farisiba kamagh…®n oraki, Iesus gumazamizir av…®riba ruez…®, gumazamizir kaba an suren gumazibar otifi. Ez…® men d…®bobonim Jon…®n suren gumazibar d…®bobonim gafira.
