\v 5 \x - \xo 4:5 \xt Jenesis 33:19; Josua 24:32\x*Egha a ghua Samarian Distrigh…®n aven itir nguibar mam…®n oto, an ziam Sikar. Ez…® Sikar…®n nguibam, a nguazir Jekop uan otarim Josep gan…®ngizim…®n borogh…®ra iti.
