\v 9 \x - \xo 4:9 \xt 2 Atriviba 17:24; Esra 4:1-5; 9:1--10:44; Nehemia 4:1-2; Luk 9:52-53; Aposel 10:28\x*Ez…® Samarian amizim kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® Judan gumazim ez…® k…® Samarian amizim. Manmaghsua, n…® d…®pam amasa na m…®gei?‚Äù (Amizir kam fo, Judaba me Samarian gumazamiziba ko itir puvat…®, kamagh…®n an akar kam Iesus m…®gei.)
