\v 14 \x - \xo 4:14 \xt Jon 6:35; 6:58; 7:38\x*Eght…® gumazim o amizir k…® dan…®ngamin d…®par kam amegham, an kuarim dughiatam…®n uam an p…®ran kogham. Puvat…®. D…®par k…® dan…®ngamin kam, a d…®pam nguazir averiam…®n ikiava otivi mogh…®n, an navir averiam…®n otivam. Egh d…®par ik…®r…®m…®rir zurara itim an…®dir kam otiv mamagh…®ra ik…®va, zurara itir ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuarim a dan…®ngam.‚Äù
\p 
