\v 27 Iesus kamagh…®n a m…®geima, dughiar kam…®n an suren gumaziba uamategha izi. Egha me an garima an amizir kam ko uaning m…®geima, me okam n…®ghn…®si. Egha tav kamagh…®n amizim…®n azarazir puvat…®, ‚ÄúN…® tizim iniasa?‚Äù
