\v 36 \x - \xo 4:36 \xt Onger Akaba 126:5-6; Daniel 12:3\x*Gumazir dagheba isim, a dat…®r…®gh…®n uan ivezim isi, egha zurara itir ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuarim bagha dagheba akufi. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, gumazir dagheba oparim ko gumazir dagheba isim aning v…®rara bar akuegham.
\v 37 Akar kam a guizbang…®ra, ‚ÄòGumazir mam azenim opari, ez…® gumazir igharazim an dagheba isi.‚Äô
\v 38 K…®, ia faragha ingarizir puvat…®zir azenim…®n dagheba iniasa, k…® ia amada. Gumazir igharaziba azenir kam…®n ingari, ez…® ia ghua me uan gavgavim…®n oparizir dagheba isi.‚Äù
