\v 42 \x - \xo 4:42 \xt Jon 17:8; 1 Jon 4:14\x*Egha me kamagh…®n amizim m…®gei, ‚ÄúE n…®n akamra baregha n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim gumazir kam…®n itir pu. Puvat…®. E uari an akam baraki, egha e fo, gumazir kamra, a guizbang…®ra nguazir kam…®n itir gumazamizibar Akurvazir Gumazim. Kamagh…®n e n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an iti.‚Äù
