\v 47 \x - \xo 4:47 \xt Matyu 8:5-6; Luk 7:1-10\x*Ez…® gumazir kam kamagh…®n oraki, Iesus Judian Distrik ategha uamategha Galilin Distrigh…®n ize. Ez…®ma a Iesus bagha ghua a gakaghora ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® Kaperneam…®n nguibam…®n mag…®r…®, nan otarim damight…®, a ua deraka. Nan otarim bar ovengasava ami.‚Äù
