\v 48 \x - \xo 4:48 \xt Jon 2:18; 20:29; 1 Korin 1:22\x*Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa mirakelba ko d…®gavir kuram gamir arazibar ganan kogh…®va, ia n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim nan ikian kogham.‚Äù
