\v 7 Ez…® ar…®mariar gumazim kamagh…®n Iesus…®n akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazir ekiam, k…® akurvazir gumaziba puvat…®. D…®pam s…®rvamadir dughiam…®n, gumazitam na inigha ghua mozir d…®pam…®n averiam gat…®zir puvat…®. K…® uab…® mangasa ifonge, ez…® gumazamizir igharaziba na gafigha faragha ghuaghiri.‚Äù
