\v 13 Ez…® gumazir ua derazir kam a fozir puvat…®, tinara a m…®keme. Dughiar kam gumazamizir av…®rim nguibar kam…®n iti, ez…® Iesus men tong…®n suiagh…®r…®gha ghu. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, gumazir kam fozir puvat…®, tina an akura.
