\v 19 \x - \xo 5:19 \xt Jon 5:30; 8:28-29; 12:49; 14:10\x*Ez…® Iesus Judabar akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, Otarim bizitam uan n…®ghn…®zim…®n a damighan kogham. Puvat…®. An Afeziam…®n gari, an amir biziba darara a dagh ami. Egha bizir Afeziam amiba, Otarim uaghan dagh ami.
\v 20 \x - \xo 5:20 \xt Matyu 3:17; Jon 3:35; 2 Pita 1:17\x*Afeziam bar Otarim gifonge, egha bizir a uab…® amiba, a bar ada isa uan Otarim…®n aka. Afeziam kamaghsua, a ia damut…® ia d…®gavir kuram damuam, kamagh…®n a ingangarir ekiar igharaziba sara uaghan uan Otarim…®n akagham, da ingangarir an amigha g…®vazibagh afiragham.
\v 21 \x - \xo 5:21 \xt God…®n Araziba 32:39; 1 Samuel 2:6; 2 Atriviba 5:7; Luk 7:14; 8:54; Jon 11:25; 11:43; Rom 4:17; Efesus 2:5\x*Afeziam gumazir ariaghirezibagh amima me ua d…®kavima an angam…®ra itir ik…®r…®m…®rim me gan…®di. Ez…® kamagh…®ra Otarim uaghan gumazir a m…®seveziba angam…®ra itir ik…®r…®m…®rim me gan…®di.
\v 22 \x - \xo 5:22 \xt Matyu 11:27; Jon 3:17; 5:27; 9:39; Aposel 10:42; 17:31; 1 Pita 4:5\x*Afeziam kot…®n gumazitam…®n araziba tuis…®zir puvat…®. Egha gumazamizibar araziba tuis…®ghamin ingangarim, an a isa Otarim gan…®ngi.
\v 23 \x - \xo 5:23 \xt Filipai 2:10-11; 1 Jon 2:23\x*Afeziam kamaghsua, gumazamiziba bar Afeziam…®n ziam fe mogh…®n, me Otarim…®n ziam fam, kamagh…®n a gumazamiziba tuis…®ghamin ingangarim isa Otarim gan…®ngi. Gumazim Otarim…®n ziam fer puvat…®, an Afeziar Otarim amadazim…®n ziam fer puvat…®.
\p 
\v 24 \x - \xo 5:24 \xt Jon 3:15-18; 6:40; 8:51; 1 Jon 3:14\x*‚ÄúK…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, gumazim nan akam baragha, egha n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Afeziar na amadazim…®n ikiava, egha a zurara itir ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuarim iti. A kotiaba puvat…®. An ovevem ategha, dat…®r…®gh…®n an angam…®ra iti.
