\v 31 \x - \xo 5:31 \xt Jon 8:13-14; Akar Mogomem 3:14\x*‚ÄúEght…® k…® uab…® ua bagh uan ingangariba ko arazibar gun m…®k…®mt…®ma, gumazamiziba n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim k…® m…®geir akar kabar ikian mark…®.\f + \fr 5:31 \ft N…® God…®n Araziba 19:15…®n gan.\f*
\v 32 \x - \xo 5:32 \xt Matyu 3:17; Jon 5:36-37; 8:18; 1 Jon 5:6-9\x*Ez…® igharazitav a iti, egha a uaghan nan araziba ko nan ingangaribar gun m…®gei. Ez…® k…® fo, a nan gun m…®geir akaba guizbang…®ra.\f + \fr 5:32 \ft Iesus ‚Äúigharazitav,‚Äù m…®g…®a, a uan Afeziam God m…®gei.\f*
