\v 33 \x - \xo 5:33-34 \xt Jon 1:19-34; 3:27-30; Efesus 2:8; Taitus 3:5\x*‚ÄúIarara fom…®ra gumazir maba amangiz…® me Jon bagha ghuez…® a nan gun m…®keme, ez…® an akam guizbang…®ra.
\v 34 K…® uab…®, k…® gavgavim gumazitam…®n akam dan…®ngasa n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®. K…® God ian akurvaghasa, k…® ifonge. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® Jon…®n akam…®n gun ia m…®gei.
\v 35 \x - \xo 5:35 \xt Matyu 13:20-21; Mak 6:20; 2 Pita 1:19\x*Jon a lam…®n m…®n ikia isia angazangarim gumazamizibagh an…®di. Ez…® dughiar otevim…®n ia an akam iniasa ifonge, ez…® Jon…®n angazangarim ia gisiragha ia gamima ia bar akonge.
