\v 36 \x - \xo 5:36 \xt Jon 3:2; 10:25; 10:38; 14:11; 1 Jon 5:9\x*‚ÄúEz…® nan gun m…®geir akar mam iti, a Jon…®n akam gafira, akar kam dat…®r…®gh…®n nan gun ia m…®gei. Afeziam, k…® ingangarir kam damuva aneg…®vasa, a na gan…®ngi. Ez…® ingangarir k…® amir kaba, da bar deraghav…®ra nan gun gumazamizibav gei, Afeziam na amadaz…® k…® ize.
\v 37 \x - \xo 5:37 \xt Matyu 3:17; 17:5; Mak 1:11; Luk 3:22; Jon 5:32; 6:27; 8:18; 1 Timoti 1:17; 1 Jon 4:12\x*Ez…® Afeziar na amadaz…® k…® izezim, a uab…® nan gun m…®gei. Ez…® ia tong an akam barazir puvat…®. Egha ia dughiatam an guam…®n ganizir puvat…®. Bar puvat…®.
\v 38 Ia Afeziam amadazir gumazir kam…®n akam n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an itir puvat…®. Ian arazir kaba ian gun m…®gei, Afeziam…®n akam uaghan ian navir averiabar itir puvat…®.\f + \fr 5:38 \ft Gumazir Afeziam amadazir kam, a Iesus uab…®.\f*
