\v 45 \x - \xo 5:45 \xt God…®n Araziba 31:26-27; Rom 2:12\x*‚ÄúIa kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®ghan mark…®, k…® Afeziam…®n damazim…®n akam ia gasam. Puvat…®. Gumazir akam ia gasamim, a Moses uab…®, a gumazir kam ia ghaze, a ian akuragham.
\v 46 \x - \xo 5:46 \xt Jenesis 3:15; God…®n Araziba 18:15-18; Jon 1:45; Aposel 3:22; 26:22\x*Ez…® akar Moses osiriziba, da nan gun m…®gei. Kamagh…®n, ia n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Moses…®n akabar ik…®va, egh ia uaghan n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim nan akabar ikiam. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia guizbang…®ra n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Moses…®n akaba ko nan akabar itir puvat…®.
\v 47 \x - \xo 5:47 \xt Luk 16:31\x*Ez…® kamagh…®n, ia n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Moses osirizir akabar itir puvat…®, egh ia manmagh…®n n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim na akabar ikiam?‚Äù
\c 6
\s1 Iesus dagheba isa 5,000plan gumazibagh an…®di
