\v 14 \x - \xo 6:14 \xt Jenesis 49:10; God…®n Araziba 18:15-18; Matyu 11:3; Jon 1:21; 2:11; 4:19; 4:25; 5:46\x*Ez…® gumazamiziba mirakel…®n arazir Iesus amizir kam…®n ganigha, kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúBar guizbang…®ra, kar God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim, God nguazir kam…®n anemangasa m…®keme!‚Äù
\v 15 \x - \xo 6:15 \xt Matyu 14:23; Jon 18:36\x*Ez…® Iesus akar kam baregha fo, me iz…®va an suiragh a damight…®, a men atrivim…®n ikiam. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a danganir kam ategha uab…®ra uamategha m…®ghs…®am…®n ghu.
