\v 26 \x - \xo 6:26 \xt Jon 6:11-12\x*Ez…® Iesus men akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúBar guizbang…®ra k…® ia m…®gei, ia mirakel…®n arazarazir ia ganiziba dagh n…®ghn…®gha iza na buri, o? Puvat…®. K…® ghaze, ia dagher k…® ia gan…®ngizir kam amegha ian naviba bar izefe, ez…® bizir kam bagha ia na buri.
\v 27 \x - \xo 6:27 \xt Matyu 3:17; Luk 3:22; Jon 1:33; 4:14; 6:48-58; Aposel 2:22; 2 Pita 1:17\x*Ia dagher kuragh…®riba bagh ingar da inian mark…®. Ia dagher zurara ikia mamagh…®ra itim bagh ingar…®va a inigh, kar dagher zurara itir ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuarim an…®dim. Afeziam God kamagh…®n ian aka, Gumazamizibar Otarim, a uab…®n torogha gavgavim a gan…®ngi. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, dagher kam, Gumazamizibar Otarim ia dan…®ngam.‚Äù
