\v 51 \x - \xo 6:51 \xt Jon 3:13; Hibru 10:5; 10:10\x*K…® uab…® dagher kam, ik…®r…®m…®rir zurara itim an…®dim, God…®n Nguibam ategha izaghir…®. Eght…® gumazitam dagher kam amegh…®va, a zurara itir ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuarim iniam. Dagher k…® a dan…®ngamim, a nan inivaf…®zim. K…® kamaghsua, nguazim…®n gumazamiziba me angam…®ra ikiam, kamagh…®n k…® me bagh uan inivaf…®zim anenigham.‚Äù
