\v 25 \x - \xo 17:25 \xt Jon 8:55; 15:21; 16:3; 16:27\x*‚ÄúN…® Arazir Aghuibaram Amir Afeziam, nguazim…®n gumazamiziba n…® g…®fozir puvat…®. Ez…® k…® n…® g…®fo. Ez…® nan adarasi, me fo, n…® na amadaz…® k…® ize.
\v 26 \x - \xo 17:26 \xt Jon 15:9; 15:15; 17:6\x*K…® kamagh…®n ifonge, me igharaz darazigh ifongezir arazim inigham, mati n…® na gifongez…® mok…®n. Eght…® k…® uaghan men aven ikiam. Kamagh…®n k…® n…® isa men aka, egh k…® kamagh…®n damu mamagh…®ra ikiam.‚Äù
