\v 1 \x - \xo 18:1 \xt 2 Samuel 15:23; Matyu 26:36; Mak 14:32; Luk 22:39\x*Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n God ko m…®kemegha g…®vagha, egha uan suren gumaziba ko me ghua Kidron…®n Zarim gir…®gha vong…®n ghue. Ez…® d…®par kam…®n vong…®n azenir mam iti, ez…® Iesus uan suren gumaziba ko me azenir kam…®n aven ghue.
\v 2 \x - \xo 18:2 \xt Luk 21:37; 22:39\x*Dughiar av…®ribar Iesus uan suren gumaziba azenir kam…®n me batifi. Kamagh…®n Judas, a Iesus is…® gumazir apanibar agharim dar…®ghamim, a uaghan azenir kam g…®fo.
\v 3 \x - \xo 18:3 \xt Matyu 26:47; Mak 14:43; Luk 22:47; Jon 7:45; Aposel 1:16\x*Egha a Rom…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba ko, ofa gamir gumazir ekiaba ko Farisiba amadazir polis…®n maba inigha me danganir kam…®n ghue. Egha me adenir aviba ko lamba ko m…®dorozir biziba sara suigha zui.
\v 4 Ez…® Iesus bizir a bativamiba a bar dagh fo. Egha a s…®vagha men borogh…®ra ghua kamagh…®n men azara, ‚ÄúIa tina buri?‚Äù
