\v 8 Ez…® Iesus kamagh…®n men akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® ia m…®kemegha g…®fa, kar k…®rara. Kamagh…®n ia na buriva, gumazir kaba ateght…® me mang…®.‚Äù
