\v 9 \x - \xo 18:9 \xt Jon 17:12\x*A kamaghsua an akar fom…®ra m…®kemezim, an daghem otogham, ‚ÄúEz…® gumazir n…® na gan…®ngiziba, men tav ovengezir puvat…®.‚Äù Kamagh…®n an arazir kam gami.
