\v 10 \x - \xo 18:10 \xt Matyu 26:51; Mak 14:47; Luk 22:38; 22:49-50\x*Ez…® Saimon Pita m…®dorozir sabar mam inigha ize, egha uan sabam a m…®k…®r…®gha ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim…®n ingangarir gumazim m…®sogha, an kuarir guvim…®n itim atuz…®, a ir…®. Ingangarir gumazir kam…®n ziam, Malkus.
\v 11 \x - \xo 18:11 \xt Matyu 20:22; 26:39; 26:42; Mak 14:36; Luk 22:42\x*Ez…® Iesus Pita m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® sabam inigh ua an nodozim darugh. Manmagh ami? N…® ghaze, k…® ti Afeziam na gan…®ngizir os…®mt…®zir kam inian kogham, o?‚Äù
\s1 Me Iesus inigha Anas bagha zui
\p 
\v 12 Ez…® Rom…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba ko men gumazir ekiam, ko Judan polis…®n gumaziba, me Iesus…®n suighava benim…®n a ike.
\v 13 \x - \xo 18:13 \xt Matyu 26:57; Luk 3:2\x*Egha faraghava a inigha Anas bagha ghu. Anas a Kaiafas…®n ivozir afeziam. Kaiafas a azenir kam…®n ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim.
\v 14 \x - \xo 18:14 \xt Jon 11:49-50\x*Egha Kaiafas, Judaba kamagh…®n me m…®kemezir gumazim, ‚ÄúKamagh…®n a dera, gumazir vam…®ra gumazamizibar danganim inigh aremegham.‚Äù
\s1 Pita ghaze, a Iesus g…®fozir puvat…®
\r (Matyu 26:69-70; Mak 14:66-68; Luk 22:55-57)
