\v 15 \x - \xo 18:15 \xt Matyu 26:58; Mak 14:54; Luk 22:54; Jon 20:3; 21:20; Aposel 3:1\x*Ez…® Saimon Pita ko suren gumazir igharazir mam, aning Iesus…®n g…®n zui. Ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim, a suren gumazir kam g…®fo, kamagh…®n amiz…®, a Iesus…®n g…®n ghua ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim…®n d…®penim…®n d…®vazim…®n aven ghu.
\v 16 \x - \xo 18:16 \xt Matyu 26:69; Mak 14:66; Luk 22:54\x*Ez…® Pita azenan ikia tiar akam…®n borogh…®ra tughav iti. Ez…® suren gumazir igharazim, a ghua amizir tiar akam…®n garim m…®kemegha, Pita inigha aven zui.
