\v 22 \x - \xo 18:22 \xt Jeremaia 20:2; Aposel 23:2\x*Iesus kamagh…®n m…®geima ez…® polis…®n gumazir mam tughav ikia, egha an an guam a m…®suegha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® kamagh…®n ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim…®n akam ikaragha ghaze, kar ti arazir aghuim, o?‚Äù
