\p Ez…® Judaba kamagh…®n an akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúE gumazitam puram a m…®sueght…® an aremeghan kogham.‚Äù\f + \fr 18:31 \ft Rom…®n gavman Judabar Nguazim gatifa. Egha me amamangat…®z…®, Judaba uari uan kot…®n aven bizitabar ak…®ram. Egha me Judabar kotiabar kamagh…®n anogoroke, me gumazitam bagh m…®k…®mt…®, an aremeghan markiam. Arazir gumazim ter ighuvim gafuz…® an aremeghamim, kar Rombar arazimra.\f*
\v 32 \x - \xo 18:32 \xt Matyu 20:19; Jon 3:14; 12:32-33\x*(Iesus fom…®ra uan ovengamin arazim m…®gei. A kamaghsua, an akar kam guizbang…®ra otivam, ez…® kamagh…®n Pailat ko Judaba kamagh…®n uariv gei, ez…® bizir kam oto.)
