\v 7 \x - \xo 19:7 \xt Ofa Gami 24:16; Matyu 26:65; Jon 5:18\x*Ez…® Judaba kamagh…®n an akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúA uab…® ghaze ‚ÄòK…® God…®n Otarim.‚Äô Ez…® en Arazibar Osizirir mam iti, ez…® arazir kam kamagh…®n m…®gei, gumazir kamagh…®n m…®geim, an aremegham.‚Äù
